{"id":74,"parent_id":52,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":74,"title":"Exodus 22","subtitle":"","short_title":"Ex.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 22"],[".studySummary",["i","The Lord reveals His laws pertaining to stealing, destructions by fire, care of the property of others, borrowing, lascivious acts, sacrifices to false gods, afflicting widows, usury, reviling God, and the firstborn of men and of animals—The men of Israel are commanded to be holy."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.1","order":"02.03.022.6773"},["b","1"],"If a man shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"steal"],"an ox, or a sheep, and kill it, or sell it; he shall",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"restore"],"five oxen for an ox, and",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_1c"},"four"],"sheep for a sheep."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.2","order":"02.03.022.6774"},["b","2"],"¶If a thief be found",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"breaking"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"up"],", and be smitten that he die,",["i","there shall"],"no blood",["i","be shed"],"for him."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.3","order":"02.03.022.6775"},["b","3"],"If the sun be risen upon him,",["i","there shall be"],"blood",["i","shed"],"for him;",["i","for"],"he should make full restitution; if he have nothing, then he shall be sold for his theft."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.4","order":"02.03.022.6776"},["b","4"],"If the theft be certainly found in his hand alive, whether it be ox, or ass, or sheep; he shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"restore"],"double."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.5","order":"02.03.022.6777"},["b","5"],"¶If a man shall cause a field or vineyard to be eaten, and shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"put"],"in his beast, and shall feed in another man’s field; of the best of his own field, and of the best of his own vineyard, shall he make restitution."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.6","order":"02.03.022.6778"},["b","6"],"¶If fire break out, and catch in thorns, so that the stacks of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"corn"],", or the standing corn, or the field, be consumed",["i","therewith;"],"he that",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"kindled"],"the fire shall surely make restitution."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.7","order":"02.03.022.6779"},["b","7"],"¶If a man shall deliver unto his neighbour money or stuff to keep, and it be stolen out of the man’s house; if the thief be found, let him pay double."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.8","order":"02.03.022.6780"},["b","8"],"If the thief be not found, then the master of the house shall be brought unto the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"judges"],",",["i","to see"],"whether he have put his hand unto his neighbour’s goods."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.9","order":"02.03.022.6781"},["b","9"],"For all manner of trespass,",["i","whether it be"],"for ox, for ass, for sheep, for raiment,",["i","or"],"for any manner of lost thing, which",["i","another"],"challengeth to be his, the cause of both parties shall come before the judges;",["i","and"],"whom the judges shall condemn, he shall pay double unto his neighbour."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.10","order":"02.03.022.6782"},["b","10"],"If a man deliver unto his neighbour an ass, or an ox, or a sheep, or any beast, to keep; and it die, or be hurt, or driven away, no man seeing",["i","it:"]],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.11","order":"02.03.022.6783"},["b","11"],["i","Then"],"shall an",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"oath"],"of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"be between them both, that he hath not put his hand unto his neighbour’s goods; and the owner of it shall accept",["i","thereof,"],"and he shall not",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"make",["i","it"],"good"],"."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.12","order":"02.03.022.6784"},["b","12"],"And if it be stolen from him, he shall make restitution unto the owner thereof."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.13","order":"02.03.022.6785"},["b","13"],"If it be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"torn"],"in pieces,",["i","then"],"let him bring it",["i","for"],"witness,",["i","and"],"he shall not make good that which was torn."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.14","order":"02.03.022.6786"},["b","14"],"¶And if a man",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"borrow"],["i",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"ought"]],"of his neighbour, and it be hurt, or die, the owner thereof",["i","being"],"not with it, he shall surely make",["i","it"],"good."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.15","order":"02.03.022.6787"},["b","15"],["i","But"],"if the owner thereof",["i","be"],"with it, he shall not make",["i","it"],"good: if it",["i","be"],"an hired",["i","thing,"],"it came for his hire."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.16","order":"02.03.022.6788"},["b","16"],"¶And if a man entice a maid that is not betrothed, and lie with her, he shall surely endow her to be his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"wife"],"."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.17","order":"02.03.022.6789"},["b","17"],"If her father utterly refuse to give her unto him, he shall pay money according to the dowry of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"virgins"],"."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.18","order":"02.03.022.6790"},["b","18"],"¶Thou shalt not suffer a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"witch"],"to live."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.19","order":"02.03.022.6791"},["b","19"],"¶Whosoever lieth with a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"beast"],"shall surely be put to death."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.20","order":"02.03.022.6792"},["b","20"],"¶He that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"sacrificeth"],"unto",["i","any"],"god, save unto the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"only, he shall be utterly destroyed."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.21","order":"02.03.022.6793"},["b","21"],"¶Thou shalt neither vex a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"stranger"],", nor",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_21b"},"oppress"],"him: for ye were",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_21c"},"strangers"],"in the land of Egypt."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.22","order":"02.03.022.6794"},["b","22"],"¶Ye shall not afflict any",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"widow"],", or fatherless child."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.23","order":"02.03.022.6795"},["b","23"],"If thou afflict them in any wise, and they cry at all unto me, I will surely hear their cry;"],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.24","order":"02.03.022.6796"},["b","24"],"And my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"wrath"],"shall",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_24b"},"wax hot"],", and I will kill you with the sword; and your wives shall be widows, and your children fatherless."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.25","order":"02.03.022.6797"},["b","25"],"¶If thou",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"lend"],"money to",["i","any of"],"my people",["i","that is"],"poor by thee, thou shalt not be to him as an usurer, neither shalt thou lay upon him",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_25b"},"usury"],"."],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.26","order":"02.03.022.6798"},["b","26"],"If thou at all take thy neighbour’s raiment to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_26a"},"pledge"],", thou shalt deliver it unto him by that the sun goeth down:"],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.27","order":"02.03.022.6799"},["b","27"],"For that",["i","is"],"his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_27a"},"covering only"],", it",["i","is"],"his raiment for his skin: wherein shall he sleep? and it shall come to pass, when he crieth unto me, that I will hear; for I",["i","am"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_27b"},"gracious"],"."],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.28","order":"02.03.022.6800"},["b","28"],"¶Thou shalt not",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_28a"},"revile"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_28b"},"the gods"],", nor",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_28c"},"curse"],"the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_28d"},"ruler"],"of thy people."],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.29","order":"02.03.022.6801"},["b","29"],"¶Thou shalt not delay",["i","to offer"],"the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_29a"},"first"],"of thy ripe fruits, and of thy",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_29b"},"liquors"],": the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_29c"},"firstborn"],"of thy sons shalt thou give unto me."],["div",{"id":"30","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.30","order":"02.03.022.6802"},["b","30"],"Likewise shalt thou do with thine oxen,",["i","and"],"with thy sheep:",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_30a"},"seven"],"days it shall be with his dam; on the eighth day thou shalt give it me."],["div",{"id":"31","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.31","order":"02.03.022.6803"},["b","31"],"¶And ye shall be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_31a"},"holy"],"men unto me: neither shall ye eat",["i","any"],"flesh",["i","that is"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_31b"},"torn"],"of beasts in the field; ye shall cast it to the dogs."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.1a","order":"02.03.022.6804"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/stealing"},"TG Stealing"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.1b","order":"02.03.022.6806"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/repent"},"TG Repent"],"."],["div",{"id":"1c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.1c","order":"02.03.022.6808"},["b","1c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/12.6"},"2 Sam. 12:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.2a","order":"02.03.022.6810"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/24.43"},"Matt. 24:43"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.2b","order":"02.03.022.6812"},["b","2b"],["span.small","OR"],"in."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.4a","order":"02.03.022.6814"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/6.31.30-31"},"Prov. 6:31 (30–31)"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.5a","order":"02.03.022.6816"},["b","5a"],["span.small","HEB"],"let his beast loose and it shall feed."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.6a","order":"02.03.022.6818"},["b","6a"],["span.small","HEB"],"grain."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.6b","order":"02.03.022.6820"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/judg/15.5"},"Judg. 15:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.8a","order":"02.03.022.6822"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/21.6"},"Ex. 21:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.11a","order":"02.03.022.6824"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/8.31"},"1 Kgs. 8:31"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/4.37.35-37"},"1 Ne. 4:37 (35–37)"],"."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.11b","order":"02.03.022.6826"},["b","11b"],["span.small","IE"],"make restitution."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.13a","order":"02.03.022.6828"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/31.39"},"Gen. 31:39"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.14a","order":"02.03.022.6830"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/borrow"},"TG Borrow"],"."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.14b","order":"02.03.022.6832"},["b","14b"],["span.small","OR"],"anything."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.16a","order":"02.03.022.6834"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/22.29.28-29"},"Deut. 22:29 (28–29)"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.17a","order":"02.03.022.6836"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/22.28"},"Deut. 22:28"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.18a","order":"02.03.022.6838"},["b","18a"],["span.small","IE"],"a sorceress or a sorcerer.",["span.small","JST"],"Ex. 22:18 …",["i","murderer"],"…",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sorcery"},"TG Sorcery"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.19a","order":"02.03.022.6840"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/59.6"},"D&C 59:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.20a","order":"02.03.022.6842"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/25.2.2,7-8"},"Num. 25:2 (2, 7–8)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/13.2.1-2,5,7"},"Deut. 13:2 (1–2, 5, 7)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/1.3.2-3"},"Ps. 1:3 (2–3)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/9.13"},"D&C 9:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.21a","order":"02.03.022.6844"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/stranger"},"TG Stranger"],"."],["div",{"id":"21b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.21b","order":"02.03.022.6846"},["b","21b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/love"},"TG Love"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/oppression"},"Oppression"],"."],["div",{"id":"21c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.21c","order":"02.03.022.6848"},["b","21c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/23.7"},"Deut. 23:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.22a","order":"02.03.022.6850"},["b","22a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/widows"},"TG Widows"],"."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.24a","order":"02.03.022.6852"},["b","24a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/32.10"},"Ex. 32:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"24b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.24b","order":"02.03.022.6854"},["b","24b"],["span.small","OR"],"be aroused."],["div",{"id":"25a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.25a","order":"02.03.022.6856"},["b","25a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/debt"},"TG Debt"],"."],["div",{"id":"25b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.25b","order":"02.03.022.6858"},["b","25b"],["span.small","OR"],"interest.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/usury"},"TG Usury"],"."],["div",{"id":"26a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.26a","order":"02.03.022.6860"},["b","26a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/24.13"},"Deut. 24:13"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.7"},"Ezek. 18:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"27a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.27a","order":"02.03.022.6862"},["b","27a"],["span.small","OR"],"only covering."],["div",{"id":"27b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.27b","order":"02.03.022.6864"},["b","27b"],["span.small","OR"],"compassionate.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/grace"},"TG Grace"],"."],["div",{"id":"28a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.28a","order":"02.03.022.6866"},["b","28a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/reviling"},"TG Reviling"],"."],["div",{"id":"28b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.28b","order":"02.03.022.6868"},["b","28b"],["span.small","JST"],"Ex. 22:28 …",["i","against God"],"…"],["div",{"id":"28c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.28c","order":"02.03.022.6870"},["b","28c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/19.21.21-22"},"2 Sam. 19:21 (21–22)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/curse"},"TG Curse"],"."],["div",{"id":"28d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.28d","order":"02.03.022.6872"},["b","28d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/citizenship"},"TG Citizenship"],"."],["div",{"id":"29a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.29a","order":"02.03.022.6874"},["b","29a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/neh/10.35"},"Neh. 10:35"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/3.9"},"Prov. 3:9"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/44.30"},"Ezek. 44:30"],"."],["div",{"id":"29b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.29b","order":"02.03.022.6876"},["b","29b"],["span.small","OR"],"outflow of the presses."],["div",{"id":"29c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.29c","order":"02.03.022.6878"},["b","29c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/firstborn"},"TG Firstborn"],"."],["div",{"id":"30a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.30a","order":"02.03.022.6880"},["b","30a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/22.27"},"Lev. 22:27"],"."],["div",{"id":"31a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.31a","order":"02.03.022.6882"},["b","31a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.6"},"Ex. 19:6"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/w-of-m/1.17"},"W of M 1:17"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/13.26"},"Alma 13:26"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/49.8"},"D&C 49:8"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/107.29"},"107:29"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/moses/7.62"},"Moses 7:62"],"."],["div",{"id":"31b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.31b","order":"02.03.022.6884"},["b","31b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/22.8"},"Lev. 22:8"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/4.14"},"Ezek. 4:14"],"."]]}
